# Project 04 – [BATTLESHIP]

 

## 🕹️ Description

 

This is a turn-based Battleship game written in C++ using SDL2. Players take turns attacking each other's grid to sink all the opponent's ships. The game features a 5x5 grid, random ship placement, and visual feedback for hits and misses. 

## 🎮 Controls

 

•	Mouse:

•	Click on a cell to attack it.

•	Keyboard:

•	Press Esc to exit the game.

 

