## ✨ Extra Features

 

•	Random ship placement at the start of the game.

•	Visual feedback:

•	Red: Hit

•	Blue: Miss

•	Green: Ship (visible only on the player's own grid).

•	Turn-based gameplay with alternating turns between Player 1 and Player 2.

•	Game over detection when all ships of one player are sunk.